cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual place recognition and classification using RGB cameras. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the proposed algorithm is tested in challenging robot place recognition tasks. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a method that integrates a Naive Bayes Nearest Neighbor model into a fully-convolutional neural network. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a method for semantic place categorization using deep learning techniques. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image classification using RGB cameras.
